data.description: Come checkout this well cared for Brester Built 3 Bedroom, 3 Bath, 2 Story home in Southwest Lincoln. As you enter, the main level features a nice open living room with new carpet, 1/2 bath, home office and dining room with solid wood floors. Kitchen features include wood floors, pantry and peninsula style island with lots of counter top space. As you head upstairs the second floor features 2 nice size bedrooms, full bath and a large primary suite with walk-in closet and primary bath. As you head downstairs the basement features a nice sized family room with built-ins and a rough-in for an additional bathroom. As you head outside the exterior features, a newer roof and newer high quality Pella windows, privacy fenced yard, patio & cover porch spaces and lots of landscaping. All this and just around the corner from Pioneers Park!
